No. 243,

Misc.

In re Smith; and Doby v. Collins et al. No. 452,

Misc.

Petitioners pro se. Hilton A. Dickson, Jr., Attorney General of New Mexico, and Carl P. Dunifon, Mark C. Reno and Norman S. Thayer, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent in No. 243, Mise.

Motions for leave to file petitions for writs of habeas corpus denied. Treating the papers submitted as petitions for writs of certiorari, certiorari is denied.
